Package affymetrix.gcos.cdf

Class Summary
CDFFileData This class provides reading and storage capabilities for the CDF file.
CDFFileHeader Stores information from the header section of the CDF file.
CDFProbeGroupInformation This class provides storage for a group of probes, also known as a block.
CDFProbeInformation This class provides storage for an individual probe in a CDF file.
CDFProbeSetInformation This class provides storage for probe set information from a CDF file.
CDFProbeSetNames This class provides storage for the list of probe set names.
CDFQCProbeInformation This class provides storage for QC probes from a CDF file.
CDFQCProbeSetInformation This class provides storage for the probes in a QC probe set.
DirectionType The direction of the target the probes are designed to interrogate.
GeneChipProbeSetType The types of probe sets in a CHP file.
GeneChipQCProbeSetType Defines the type of QC probe set in a CDF file.
